#: main/templates/main/index.html:151
msgid "Mengapa Kita Membutuhkan Anonimitas di Era Digital?"
msgstr "Why Do We Need Anonymity in the Digital Era?"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:155
msgid ""
"Di era media sosial yang serba terbuka, di mana setiap unggahan dan komentar"
" selalu dihakimi berdasarkan nama dan identitas fisik, manusia seringkali "
"kehilangan keberanian untuk menyuarakan pikiran atau pujian yang paling "
"murni. Fenomena ini menciptakan budaya ketakutan akan penilaian sosial "
"(<em>Social Judgment Fear</em>)."
msgstr ""
"In an era of open social media, where every post and comment is always "
"judged by name and physical identity, people often lose the courage to voice"
" their purest thoughts or praises. This phenomenon creates a culture of fear"
" of social judgment (<em>Social Judgment Fear</em>)."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:158
msgid ""
"CurhatBox hadir sebagai antitesis terhadap tekanan tersebut. Dengan "
"menghilangkan identitas pengirim, kita menormalisasi pertukaran kritik yang "
"membangun, permintaan maaf yang selama ini terpendam, serta apresiasi tulus "
"tanpa tendensi mencari muka. Psikologi anonimitas membantu melepaskan beban "
"citra diri, sehingga komunikasi yang terjadi jauh lebih autentik, jujur, dan"
" tidak berdasar pada bias status sosial sang pengirim."
msgstr ""
"CurhatBox arrives as an antithesis to that pressure. By removing the "
"sender's identity, we normalize constructive criticism, long-buried "
"apologies, and sincere appreciation without the tendency of seeking "
"approval. The psychology of anonymity helps release the burden of self-"
"image, making communication much more authentic, honest, and not based on "
"the sender's social status bias."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:161
msgid ""
"Namun, kebebasan tanpa batas dapat memicu toksisitas. Itulah sebabnya "
"CurhatBox secara eksklusif menggabungkan sistem perlindungan identitas "
"mutlak dengan algoritma filter perundungan siber (<em>Cyberbullying "
"Filter</em>) untuk menciptakan ruang aman (<em>Safe Space</em>) yang "
"memberdayakan, bukan menjatuhkan."
msgstr ""
"However, limitless freedom can trigger toxicity. That is why CurhatBox "
"exclusively combines absolute identity protection with a <em>Cyberbullying "
"Filter</em> algorithm to create an empowering, not degrading, <em>Safe "
"Space</em>."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:175
msgid "Ekspresi jujur bebas dari validasi eksternal."
msgstr "Honest expression free from external validation."

