#: main/templates/main/index.html:222
msgid "Terima Pesan Anonim"
msgstr "Receive Anonymous Messages"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:224
msgid ""
"Terima pesan real-time. Balas dengan emoji, atau bagikan screenshot estetik "
"ke media sosial."
msgstr ""
"[EN] Terima pesan real-time. Balas dengan emoji, atau bagikan screenshot "
"estetik ke media sosial."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:231
msgid "Misi Keamanan Kami"
msgstr "Our Security Mission"

#: main/templates/main/index.html:233
msgid ""
"Di CurhatBox, kami percaya bahwa kebebasan berpendapat tidak boleh "
"mengorbankan kesehatan mental. Itulah sebabnya kami menerapkan algoritma "
"penyaringan otomatis untuk mencegah perundungan (cyberbullying)."
msgstr ""
"At CurhatBox, we believe that freedom of speech should not sacrifice mental "
"health. That is why we implement an automatic harsh word filtering "
"algorithm. Every incoming message passes through strict filters to ensure no"
" cyberbullying occurs on our platform."

#: main/templates/main/index.html:236
msgid ""
"Gunakan fitur <strong>Blokir IP</strong> untuk menghentikan oknum yang "
"menyalahgunakan anonimitas secara permanen."
msgstr ""
"Use the <strong>IP Block</strong> feature to permanently stop individuals "
"who abuse anonymity."

