#: main/templates/main/rules.html:47
msgid "I. Kebijakan Privasi & Enkripsi Data"
msgstr "I. Privacy Policy & Data Encryption"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:57
msgid ""
"Kepercayaan Anda adalah segalanya. Kami mengadopsi standar keamanan mutakhir"
" untuk melindungi hak anonimitas dan rekam jejak Anda:"
msgstr ""
"Your trust is everything. We adopt cutting-edge security standards to "
"protect your anonymity rights and track record:"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:59
msgid "⚙️ Fitur Keamanan Proaktif"
msgstr "⚙️ Proactive Security Features"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:61
msgid ""
"<li><strong>Identitas Super Rahasia:</strong> Nama, Email, dan informasi "
"sensitif pengirim tidak akan pernah bocor ke layar penerima.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>Super Secret Identity:</strong> The sender's Name, Email, and "
"sensitive information will never leak to the recipient's screen.</li>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:62
msgid ""
"<li><strong>Sistem Sender Hints (Pelacakan OS):</strong> Meski nama "
"disembunyikan, sistem kami mendeteksi tipe Perangkat/Browser (contoh: "
"<em>Chrome on Android</em>) sebagai \"petunjuk\" mitigasi agar penerima "
"tidak diteror oleh entitas asing.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>Sender Hints System (OS Tracking):</strong> Although names are "
"hidden, our system detects Device/Browser types (e.g., <em>Chrome on "
"Android</em>) as a mitigation \"hint\" so that recipients are not terrorized"
" by foreign entities.</li>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:63
msgid ""
"<li><strong>Mode Pesan Sekali Baca (Self-Destruct):</strong> Untuk Pesan "
"berlogo 💣, pesan tersebut akan dihapus keras dari database kami sesaat "
"setelah dibaca. Tidak ada rekam jejak pemulihan!</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>One-Time Read Mode (Self-Destruct):</strong> For messages with "
"the 💣 logo, the message will be hard deleted from our database immediately "
"after being read. No recovery record!</li>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:64
msgid ""
"<li><strong>Proteksi Anti-Spam (Rate Limiting):</strong> Kami secara agresif"
" menolak koneksi ganda atau pengiriman pesan beruntun dari Alamat IP yang "
"sama dalam durasi tidak wajar.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>Anti-Spam Protection (Rate Limiting):</strong> We aggressively "
"reject multiple connections or sequential message sending from the same IP "
"Address within an unreasonable duration.</li>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:66
msgid "📜 Kepatuhan Hukum & Data Forensik"
msgstr "📜 Legal Compliance & Forensic Data"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:67
msgid ""
"<p class=\"text-body-secondary\">Sistem mencatat Alamat IP pengirim murni "
"untuk keperluan <strong>Audit Forensik</strong>. Jika terjadi kejahatan "
"pidana berat, log data tersebut akan diserahkan secara eksklusif kepada "
"Aparat Penegak Hukum berwenang.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p class=\"text-body-secondary\">The system records the sender's IP Address "
"purely for <strong>Forensic Audit</strong> purposes. In case of serious "
"criminal offense, the log data will be submitted exclusively to authorized "
"Law Enforcement Officers.</p>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:82
msgid "II. Etika & Ketentuan Layanan"
msgstr "II. Ethics & Terms of Service"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:91
msgid ""
"<p>Layanan CurhatBox dirancang khusus pengguna berusia <strong>13 tahun ke "
"atas</strong>. Sebagai wadah publik jujur, mari jaga norma bersosial "
"media:</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>The CurhatBox service is designed specifically for users aged <strong>13 "
"or older</strong>. As an honest public forum, let's maintain social media "
"norms:</p>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:93
msgid "🚫 Toleransi Nol (Zero Tolerance) Pelanggaran Siber:"
msgstr "🚫 Zero Tolerance for Cyber Violations:"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:95
msgid ""
"Perundungan siber (*Cyberbullying*), pemerasan, atau ancaman kekerasan."
msgstr "Cyberbullying, extortion, or threats of violence."

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:96
msgid "Ujaran kebencian (*Hate Speech*), rasisme, atau provokasi massal."
msgstr "Hate speech, racism, or mass provocation."

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:97
msgid "Penyebaran materi pornografi, asusila, atau konten vulgar (18+)."
msgstr "Spread of pornographic, immoral, or vulgar content (18+)."

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:98
msgid "Di atas segalanya, dilarang menyebarkan privasi orang lain (*Doxing*)."
msgstr "Above all, it is forbidden to spread other people's privacy (Doxing)."

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:101
msgid "🔨 Mandat Moderasi & Blokir Mandiri"
msgstr "🔨 Moderation Mandate & Self-Block"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:102
msgid ""
"<p class=\"text-body-secondary\">Pengguna dapat langsung menggunakan fitur "
"<strong>Blokir Permanen (Self-Ban)</strong> untuk menghentikan pesan "
"lanjutan dari pelaku teror.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p class=\"text-body-secondary\">Users can immediately use the "
"<strong>Permanent Block (Self-Ban)</strong> feature to stop further messages"
" from harassers.</p>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:117
msgid "III. Penyangkalan & Batas Tanggung Jawab"
msgstr "III. Disclaimer & Limitation of Liability"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:126
msgid ""
"<p>Layanan CurhatBox berstatus <em>\"AS IS\" (Sebagaimana Adanya)</em>. Kami"
" merupakan medium penyedia komunikasi, bukan penanggung jawab ucapan.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>The CurhatBox service is provided <em>\"AS IS\"</em>. We are a medium for"
" communication, not responsible for speech.</p>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:127
msgid ""
"<p>Kami <strong>TERBEBAS SECARA HUKUM</strong> atas segala kerugian "
"materiil, gangguan psikis, guncangan mental, maupun reputasi tercemar yang "
"disebabkan oleh tulisan individu di dalam platform ini. Tanggung jawab nyata"
" bersandar pada ketikan si Pengirim sesuai koridor Undang-Undang ITE "
"Republik Indonesia.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>We are <strong>LEGALLY EXEMPT</strong> from all material losses, "
"psychological disturbances, mental shocks, or tarnished reputations caused "
"by individual writing within this platform. Real responsibility rests on the"
" Sender's typing according to the corridors of the Republic of Indonesia ITE"
" Law.</p>"

#: main/templates/main/rules.html:138
msgid "Tim Legal atau Pertanyaan? Hubungi Meja Layanan:"
msgstr "Legal Team or Questions? Contact Service Desk:"

